Story_Texts.SourceString: The Skyfall devastated this area. There are craters everywhere.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The Skyfall devastated this area. There are craters everywhere.

Story_Texts.SourceString: There was a floating city of light here.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: There was a floating city of light here.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Crystal meteors destroyed the floating city,
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Crystal meteors destroyed the floating city,

Story_Texts.SourceString: Yang was the guardian of the Celestial gate to the plane of light.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Yang was the guardian of the Celestial gate to the plane of light.

Story_Texts.SourceString: He must have been corrupted by Zerath.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: He must have been corrupted by Zerath.

Story_Texts.SourceString: We need to free him if there is ever a chance for this city to fly again.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: We need to free him if there is ever a chance for this city to fly again.
